---
import InvestLayout from '../layouts/InvestLayout.astro';
import Disclosure from '../components/Disclosure.astro';
---

<InvestLayout
  title="Governance"
  titleVi="Quản trị"
  description="Nguyen AI Computer governance: cap table placeholder, board structure, IP ownership (HoldCo model), and decision rights."
>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">Governance</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Quản trị</p>

    <!-- Cap table placeholder -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Cap Table</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">Bảng cơ cấu cổ phần</p>
      <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-gold border border-gold/30 rounded-full">Placeholder</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-ink-dim" lang="vi">Dữ liệu mẫu — chưa công bố</span>
        </div>
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-bg-border">
              <th class="text-left py-3 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Stakeholder / Cổ đông</th>
              <th class="text-right py-3 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Pre-money</th>
              <th class="text-right py-3 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Post-money</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-bg-border">
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink">Founder(s) / Nhà sáng lập</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right text-gold">100%</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right text-gold">85.71%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink">Seed investors / Nhà đầu tư</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">0%</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right text-gold">14.29%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink">Option pool / Cổ phần dự phòng</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">TBD</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">TBD</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-ink-dim italic">
          Detailed cap table available in the private data room for qualified investors. No real cap table data in public HTML.
          <span class="block" lang="vi">Bảng cơ cấu chi tiết có trong data room riêng tư. Không có dữ liệu thật trong HTML công khai.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Board structure -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Board Structure</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">Cấu trúc hội đồng</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          { role: 'Founder seat', vi: 'Ghế nhà sáng lập', desc: 'CEO/Founder' },
          { role: 'Investor seat(s)', vi: 'Ghế nhà đầu tư', desc: 'To be determined with seed round' },
          { role: 'Independent seat', vi: 'Ghế độc lập', desc: 'To be appointed' },
        ].map((b) => (
          <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-lg p-5 card-hover">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink">{b.role}</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-ink-dim" lang="vi">{b.vi}</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-2">{b.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- IP ownership (HoldCo) -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">IP Ownership — HoldCo Model</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">Sở hữu IP — mô hình HoldCo</p>
      <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">
          Intellectual property is held by a Holding Company (HoldCo), which licenses IP to operating entities. This structure separates IP ownership from operational risk and enables flexible entity structuring across jurisdictions.
          <span class="block mt-2" lang="vi">Sở hữu trí tuệ được nắm bởi công ty holding (HoldCo), cấp phép IP cho các thực thể vận hành. Cấu trúc này tách sở hữu IP khỏi rủi ro vận hành.</span>
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-bg-soft rounded-lg border border-bg-border">
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-dim italic">
            IP ownership transfer is pending. No IP has been formally transferred to any entity yet. This is a known risk (see Risk Register).
            <span class="block mt-1" lang="vi">Việc chuyển nhượng IP đang hoàn thiện. Chưa có IP nào được chuyển nhượng chính thức. Đây là rủi ro đã biết.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Decision rights -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Decision Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">Quyền quyết định</p>
      <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {[
            { level: 'Founder/CEO', vi: 'Nhà sáng lập/CEO', rights: 'Day-to-day operations, product, hiring, strategy' },
            { level: 'Board', vi: 'Hội đồng', rights: 'Major financing, IP transfer, entity formation, key hires' },
            { level: 'Investors', vi: 'Nhà đầu tư', rights: 'Information rights, protective provisions per term sheet' },
          ].map((d) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold mt-1">▸</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-semibold text-ink">{d.level}</span>
                <span class="text-ink-dim text-xs ml-2" lang="vi">{d.vi}</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">{d.rights}</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12"><Disclosure /></div>
  </section>
</InvestLayout>
